{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ARIA techniques","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>O ARIA define as semânticas que podem ser aplicadas aos elementos, e são divididas em <strong>funções</strong> (definindo um tipo de elemento da interface do usuário) e <strong>estados</strong> e <strong>propriedades</strong> que são suportados por uma função. Os autores devem atribuir uma função ARIA e os estados e propriedades apropriados a um elemento durante seu ciclo de vida, a menos que o elemento já possua semântica ARIA apropriada (através do uso de um elemento HTML apropriado). A adição de semântica ARIA apenas expõe informações extras para a API de acessibilidade de um navegador e não afeta o DOM de uma página.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções","title":"Funções","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_de_widget","title":"Funções de widget","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/button_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">button (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/checkbox_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">checkbox (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/gridcell_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">gridcell (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_link_role\">link</a></li>\n  <li>menuitem</li>\n  <li>menuitemcheckbox</li>\n  <li>menuitemradio</li>\n  <li>option</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_progressbar_role\">progressbar</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_radio_role\">radio</a></li>\n  <li>scrollbar</li>\n  <li>searchbox</li>\n  <li>separator (when focusable)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_slider_role\">slider</a></li>\n  <li>spinbutton</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/switch_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">switch (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tab_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tab (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tabpanel_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabpanel (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_textbox_role\">textbox</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/treeitem_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">treeitem (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_compostas","title":"Funções compostas","isH3":true,"content":"<p>As técnicas abaixo descrevem cada função composta, bem como suas funções filho obrigatórias e opcionais.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>combobox</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/grid_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid (en-US)</a> (incluindo as funções <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/row_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/gridcell_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">gridcell (en-US)</a>, rowheader, columnheader)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_listbox_role\">listbox</a> (incluindo a função option)</li>\n  <li>menu</li>\n  <li>menubar</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_radio_role\">radiogroup (veja a função radio)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tablist_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tablist (en-US)</a> (incluindo as funções <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tab_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tab (en-US)</a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tabpanel_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tabpanel (en-US)</a>)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tree_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tree (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>treegrid</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_da_estrutura_de_documento","title":"Funções da estrutura de documento","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/application_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">application (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/article_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">article (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/cell_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">cell (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>columnheader</li>\n  <li>definition</li>\n  <li>directory</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/document_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">document (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>feed</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/figure_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">figure (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_group_role\">group</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/heading_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">heading (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/Role_Img\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">img</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/list_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">list (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/listitem_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">listitem (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>math</li>\n  <li>none</li>\n  <li>note</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_presentation_role\">presentation</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/row_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/rowgroup_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">rowgroup (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>rowheader</li>\n  <li>separator</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/table_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">table (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li>term</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/textbox_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">textbox (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_toolbar_role\">toolbar</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/tooltip_role\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tooltip (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funções_de_ponto_de_referência","title":"Funções de ponto de referência","isH3":true,"